'''Neutrinos''' were near massless particles emitted by [[Star/Legends|stars]]. They were utilized with [[Neutrino radiator/Legends|neutrino radiators]]. [[Gotal/Legends|Gotals]] had the ability to sense them, whereas most other beings could not.

